{"id": 1003, "genre": 1000, "title": "如何调味让你更像一个中产阶级？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。好奇心研究所会不定期推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5677, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130129yGF38PErRjTNzHkt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-24T01:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 885, "title": "如何调味让你更像一个中产阶级？", "content": "如何调味让你更像一个中产阶级\r\n", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 79935, "content": "囤积异域香料，但很少用完", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183243ICNF1QhWxrjOUHKM.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 79946, "content": "不用速食沙拉酱拌沙拉", "image": "img/option/option/20160703130008HOJxyqSgBDKIXc9v.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 79937, "content": "善用新奇搭配，做烘焙加撮海盐 ", "image": "img/option/option/201607021830319VyKsqRlWQJmz3H5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 79938, "content": "绝对不能使用味精", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183243zgrHYQKmnS8wE49a.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 79940, "content": " 浓汤必须自己熬制的，绝不用浓汤宝", "image": "img/option/option/20160703130007OVbDrM9k5CEYNnqs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 79942, "content": "黑胡椒决不能买粉状的，要准备研磨瓶随用随磨", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183243Akl6xaL0YIUZeET5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 79944, "content": "用各种平常炒菜不会用的油：核桃油，杜松子油等", "image": "img/option/option/201607021832439mbtGOiqE8FyXvlJ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 79948, "content": "拥有全套厨房量器", "image": "img/option/option/201607021830076RPd2ISs5tgfA4M0.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}